'''Sally Horton''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[Venice Cup]] (1) 1985 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (3) 1984, 1989, 1990 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (3)
** 0 (3) 1984, 1989, 1990 

===Runners-up===

* [[World Team Olympiad|World Olympiad Womens Teams Championship]] (1) 1984

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (1) 1991 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
** 0 (1) 1991 

